         python3-pydantic (>= 2.0.0)
Recommends: python3-pyqt6 (>= 6.5.0)
Description: ARCRO - Advanced RAUC Control & Rollout Operations
 ARCRO is a comprehensive tool for deploying RAUC bundles to target
 devices. It provides both command-line and graphical user interfaces for
 managing over-the-air updates on embedded Linux systems.
 .
 Features include:
  - SSH-based connection management
  - Secure bundle transfer via SCP
  - Real-time progress monitoring
  - GUI interface with Qt6 QML (optional)
  - Comprehensive logging and error handling
 .
 This package provides the core CLI functionality. Install python3-pyqt6
 for the graphical interface.